Author: Avecletrait
Text: Yeah, eventually I realised that I can't keep this a secret and that I need to talk to someone. Turns out one of my best friends has gone through a similar thing and she wasn't jugemental about it either. I am still on this dark bumpy road but I will be able to take the next exit and hopefully get better again.  I am sorry to hear that this problem has turned your life around so badly. You must have been in a lot of pain in the past and maybe even in the present.

Author: kawaiikittenboy
Text: And that's how it all starts. It will be a dark bumpy path but I suggest you get help as soon as you can. My ED has lost me my job, friends, significant others and family. You don't ever think you'll be that person but it will twist your head so bad
